### Breakdown of Key Files:
- **`index.html`** â†’ Homepage with an introduction, course highlights, and testimonials.  
- **`about.html`** â†’ Information about Cyber Code Academy.  
- **`courses.html`** â†’ List of available IT courses.  
- **`contact.html`** â†’ Contact form with email & phone details.  
- **`signup.html`** â†’ User registration and login form.  
- **`assets/css/style.css`** â†’ Main stylesheet.  
- **`assets/js/script.js`** â†’ JavaScript for interactivity.  
- **`includes/`** â†’ Contains reusable components like the header, footer, and navbar (optional).  

